orderTips: All burgers are 1/2 lb Angus beef — ask for no bun, served on a plate
Wings are your best bet — 19 sauces available. Best low-carb sauces: buffalo, garlic parm, old bay dry rub, salt & vinegar dry rub, sour cream & onion dry rub
Avoid sweet wing sauces: sweet & sour, maple bacon, honey garlic, Mississippi honey BBQ, sweet chili, teriyaki, and Asian
Sub coleslaw ($1.00 extra) instead of fries with any burger or sandwich
Salads: always skip croutons and get dressing on the side
The Steakhouse Salad with 7oz rib-eye is a great keto meal
